Travelling Salesman Problem


road("tampa","hosan",100).
road("hosan","Vicf",120).
road("hosan","kansas_city",120).
route(Town1,Town2,Distance):-
    road(Town1,Town2,Distance).
route(Town1,Town2,Distance):-
    road(Town1,X,Dist1),
    route(X,Town2,Dist2),
    Distance is Dist1+Dist2,
    !.


Output:
?-route("tampa", "kansas_city", X),
|    write("Distance from Tampa to Kansas City is"),
|    write(X),nl.
Distance from Tampa to Kansas City is 220
X = 220.
